instructions:----------
public int subtract(int a, int b){
          return a - b;
        }
            

Use the method defined above to subtract 10 from 100 (as in 100 - 10).
----------

[systems]
language: Java

[.assets.code.wrapper.files]
content:----------
public class Syntax8to10 {
    private int aVal;
    private int bVal;

    public int subtract(int a, int b){
        aVal = a;
        bVal = b;
        return a - b;
      }

    public void run() {
        ___
    }

    public int getA() {
        return aVal;
    }

    public int getB() {
        return bVal;
    }

}
